<l>kaṇṭāṅ kaluḻva tevaṉkolō taṇṭānōy </l>
<l>tāṅkāṭṭa yāṅkaṇ ṭatu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As this incurable malady has been caused by my eyes which showed (him) to me, why should they now weep for (him).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
